00:30:00.684 --> 00:30:03.443 line:82%
Oh, very good. Very good. You
started pulling pranks again.

430
00:30:03.564 --> 00:30:04.265 line:82%
Exactly.

431
00:30:04.355 --> 00:30:06.027 line:82%
They called me to
school on the first day itself.

432
00:30:06.164 --> 00:30:08.402 line:82%
Tell him something or
else he will be rusticated.

433
00:30:09.284 --> 00:30:10.843 line:82%
And how is your work going on?

434
00:30:10.940 --> 00:30:13.898 line:82%
Anjali, the workload is
quite heavy, I might come late.

435
00:30:14.464 --> 00:30:15.943 line:82%
- Did you set everything in the house?
- No.

436
00:30:16.363 --> 00:30:17.802 line:82%
The luggage has arrived from the cargo.

437
00:30:17.983 --> 00:30:19.503 line:82%
But I just can't find a maid.

438
00:30:19.663 --> 00:30:21.423 line:82%
Everyone is scared because
of the legend of the ghost.

439
00:30:21.583 --> 00:30:23.022 line:82%
And ghosts don't exist.

440
00:30:24.943 --> 00:30:26.423 line:82%
There can't be any
better ghost than him.

441
00:30:34.624 --> 00:30:36.222 line:82%
- Good night.
- Good night.

442
00:31:12.943 --> 00:31:13.983 line:82%
Ice-cream.

443
00:31:42.264 --> 00:31:46.542 line:82%
Mama.

444
00:31:48.384 --> 00:31:49.422 line:82%
Banku.

445
00:31:49.543 --> 00:31:50.583 line:82%
Mama.

446
00:31:51.504 --> 00:31:55.782 line:82%
- Banku, what happened?
- I just saw someone here.

447
00:31:55.840 --> 00:31:57.999 line:82%
- Where?
- There.

448
00:32:03.223 --> 00:32:04.623 line:82%
But what were you doing here?

449
00:32:04.944 --> 00:32:06.983 line:82%
I just took out some
ice-cream and I turned...

450
00:32:07.124 --> 00:32:12.002 line:82%
- Ice-cream? Didn't I tell you not to?
- Just a little.

451
00:32:12.444 --> 00:32:16.802 line:82%
And that also spilled down...
Hey, where is the bowl?

452
00:32:22.844 --> 00:32:25.283 line:82%
Mama, the bowl and
spoon were right here.

453
00:32:25.604 --> 00:32:27.482 line:82%
First, you ate
ice-cream without asking me...

454
00:32:28.364 --> 00:32:29.963 line:82%
and on the top of that,
you say you saw someone?

455
00:32:30.363 --> 00:32:31.763 line:82%
It's true. I saw someone here.

456
00:32:31.964 --> 00:32:34.963 line:82%
I told you about the angel and
you started spinning a tale.

457
00:32:35.244 --> 00:32:37.082 line:82%
You'll start crying if I hit you now.

458
00:32:37.244 --> 00:32:38.402 line:82%
Just go upstairs.

459
00:32:38.924 --> 00:32:41.282 line:82%
And don't touch the
fridge without my permission.

460
00:32:42.204 --> 00:32:43.802 line:82%
How will you get up early
in the morning for school?

461
00:32:44.163 --> 00:32:45.683 line:82%
Forget you, how will I get up?

462
00:32:46.083 --> 00:32:47.243 line:82%
You've become so mischievous.

463
00:32:47.643 --> 00:32:49.283 line:82%
You should be sent
to a boarding school.

464
00:32:49.404 --> 00:32:54.242 line:82%
Hey. Let's go upstairs.
So much drama for some ice-cream.

465
00:32:54.324 --> 00:32:55.363 line:82%
Someone's there.

466
00:32:55.884 --> 00:32:57.403 line:82%
Now why are you looking here and there?

467
00:32:57.483 --> 00:32:58.802 line:82%
Come on, come upstairs.

468
00:33:00.784 --> 00:33:05.062 line:82%
I opened the fridge,
took out the ice-cream.

469
00:33:07.343 --> 00:33:11.902 line:82%
The bowl fell from my hand,
then where did it go?

470
00:33:17.063 --> 00:33:18.103 line:82%
Look at this.

471
00:33:18.152 --> 00:33:20.613 line:82%
I said that the bowl
has fallen over here...

472
00:33:20.743 --> 00:33:22.302 line:82%
but mama doesn't believe me.

473
00:34:10.583 --> 00:34:12.183 line:82%
You had hidden the bowl, hadn't you?

474
00:34:15.344 --> 00:34:17.663 line:82%
You have come to steal
the ice-cream?

475
00:34:20.924 --> 00:34:25.323 line:82%
Okay, so you are Anthony,
who was beaten up by mama.

476
00:34:25.983 --> 00:34:27.103 line:82%
I am a ghost.

477
00:34:27.749 --> 00:34:32.868 line:82%
Ghosts don't exist.
Mama said that angels exist.

478
00:34:33.516 --> 00:34:35.716 line:82%
Okay, so you're an angel.

479
00:34:36.303 --> 00:34:37.382 line:82%
I said I am a ghost.

480
00:34:38.424 --> 00:34:39.463 line:82%
I said ghosts don't exist.

481
00:34:39.903 --> 00:34:41.903 line:82%
Okay, so you have come to stay here.

482
00:34:42.170 --> 00:34:43.528 line:82%
No. This is my house.

483
00:34:44.397 --> 00:34:45.755 line:82%
I have come here to
drive you out from here.

484
00:34:46.224 --> 00:34:47.303 line:82%
This is our house.

485
00:34:47.645 --> 00:34:48.685 line:82%
This is my house.

486
00:34:48.791 --> 00:34:51.550 line:82%
- This is our house. Softly, softly.
- I said this is my house.

487
00:34:51.624 --> 00:34:54.992 line:82%
If mama hears us, then this
won't remain anybody's house.

488
00:34:55.090 --> 00:34:58.768 line:82%
You little boy, you talk too much.

489
00:34:59.343 --> 00:35:02.063 line:82%
Wait. Little boy.
I will teach him a lesson.

490
00:35:03.063 --> 00:35:06.263 line:82%
You tall fellow, my
name is Banku. And yours?

491
00:35:07.177 --> 00:35:09.775 line:82%
Didn't you see my name
outside at the gate? Nath.

492
00:35:10.704 --> 00:35:11.983 line:82%
Sometimes you say you
are a 'Bhoot' (Ghost)...

493
00:35:12.063 --> 00:35:13.103 line:82%
sometimes you say you are Nath.

494
00:35:13.743 --> 00:35:16.022 line:82%
Okay, is your name Bhootnath?

495
00:35:16.143 --> 00:35:18.062 line:82%
I am a ghost and not Bhootnath.

496
00:35:18.381 --> 00:35:19.781 line:82%
This is my house. Come on,
get out of here.

497
00:35:20.223 --> 00:35:23.822 line:82%
I said it's our house,
but you can stay here.

498
00:35:24.144 --> 00:35:25.622 line:82%
I'll convince mama.

499
00:35:27.104 --> 00:35:29.903 line:82%
So you won't agree like that.
I'll have to do something.

500
00:35:30.381 --> 00:35:31.421 line:82%
What will you do?

501
00:35:32.253 --> 00:35:33.291 line:82%
Wait. I'll tell you.

502
00:35:53.823 --> 00:35:55.742 line:82%
Hey, why are you laughing?

503
00:35:55.983 --> 00:35:58.183 line:82%
- You're making funny faces.
- Funny faces?

504
00:35:58.544 --> 00:36:00.383 line:82%
Of course. If you take part
in a fancy dress competition...

505
00:36:00.464 --> 00:36:01.502 line:82%
you'll win the first prize.

506
00:36:02.624 --> 00:36:03.983 line:82%
He's a strange child.
The whole world is scared...

507
00:36:04.064 --> 00:36:05.102 line:82%
of me and he laughs at me.

508
00:36:05.984 --> 00:36:08.623 line:82%
Hey, I am trying to scare you.
Don't you get scared?

509
00:36:09.264 --> 00:36:11.303 line:82%
- Do you get scared?
- Why should I get scared?

510
00:36:17.384 --> 00:36:21.302 line:82%
Everyone says a ghost
resides here. Have you seen him?

511
00:36:21.423 --> 00:36:22.463 line:82%
Why would I see him?

512
00:36:22.584 --> 00:36:25.583 line:82%
But don't get scared.
I stay in this room with mama.

513
00:36:25.704 --> 00:36:27.302 line:82%
If you get scared, then just call me.

514
00:36:27.903 --> 00:36:28.982 line:82%
Now we are friends, aren't we?

515
00:36:31.709 --> 00:36:32.748 line:82%
Friends?

516
00:36:33.504 --> 00:36:34.823 line:82%
- One more thing.
- What?

517
00:36:35.184 --> 00:36:37.142 line:82%
- Come closer.
- What?

518
00:36:37.224 --> 00:36:38.263 line:82%
I want to go to the bathroom.

519
00:36:39.104 --> 00:36:41.023 line:82%
- Bathroom?
- Bathroom.

520
00:36:41.664 --> 00:36:43.423 line:82%
- Then go.
- Come with me.

521
00:36:43.544 --> 00:36:44.582 line:82%
You go. Why would I come with you?

522
00:36:51.144 --> 00:36:58.223 line:82%
Am I... a ghost... or not?

523
00:37:02.893 --> 00:37:03.932 line:82%
Even you want to go to
the bathroom, don't you?

524
00:37:04.093 --> 00:37:05.772 line:82%
Hey, quiet, go away.

525
00:37:18.891 --> 00:37:20.570 line:82%
Glory to Lord Hanuman (Indian God).
Ocean of wisdom and virtue...

526
00:37:22.064 --> 00:37:23.423 line:82%
Glory to Lord Hanuman.
Ocean of wisdom and virtue...

527
00:37:25.143 --> 00:37:28.423 line:82%
Hey... Hey...

528
00:37:34.904 --> 00:37:38.222 line:82%
He got scared. I am a ghost.

529
00:37:40.383 --> 00:37:42.062 line:82%
Now I'll teach a
lesson to this little one.

530
00:37:53.411 --> 00:37:55.891 line:82%
Little boy, you're sleeping.
Come on, get up.

531
00:37:56.104 --> 00:37:57.783 line:82%
- Let me sleep.
- Get up. Get up. Get up.

532
00:37:57.983 --> 00:38:00.583 line:82%
- Let me sleep.
- Get up. I said get up.

533
00:38:01.739 --> 00:38:06.219 line:82%
He slept. Now how will he get up?

534
00:38:16.634 --> 00:38:20.033 line:82%
Wake up, Banku... Banku.

535
00:38:25.617 --> 00:38:30.176 line:82%
Hey, he went down again.

536
00:38:33.199 --> 00:38:34.423 line:82%
Ice-cream.

537
00:38:41.224 --> 00:38:44.542 line:82%
- My naughty angel.
- Angel.

538
00:38:48.664 --> 00:38:51.903 line:82%
- You know who had hidden this bowl?
- Who?

539
00:38:52.103 --> 00:38:54.502 line:82%
Angel. An angel resides
in our house.

540
00:38:54.743 --> 00:38:58.183 line:82%
Really? Then he must have
eaten this ice-cream, too.

541
00:38:58.424 --> 00:39:00.583 line:82%
No, he didn't. I even asked him.

542
00:39:00.743 --> 00:39:04.383 line:82%
Now he will stay here with us.
Now I am his friend.

543
00:39:05.303 --> 00:39:08.983 line:82%
Good, I will tell the angel
to brush your teeth everyday...

544
00:39:09.064 --> 00:39:10.903 line:82%
help you with your
homework and take you to school.

545
00:39:11.183 --> 00:39:12.223 line:82%
Alone?

546
00:39:15.184 --> 00:39:18.423 line:82%
- And you know what he said?
- Tell me that afterwards.

547
00:39:18.503 --> 00:39:19.582 line:82%
You're getting late
for school. Come on.

548
00:39:19.984 --> 00:39:21.964 line:82%
Mama, it's not a story.
This angel really exists.

549
00:39:22.004 --> 00:39:24.369 line:82%
Yes, I am not denying it.
Okay, listen there shouldn't...

550
00:39:24.783 --> 00:39:27.182 line:82%
be any complaints about
you in school today. Okay?

551
00:39:27.472 --> 00:39:28.512 line:82%
- Bye, Mama.
- Bye.

552
00:39:28.623 --> 00:39:29.661 line:82%
Bye, angel.

553
00:39:30.263 --> 00:39:33.622 line:82%
You and your angel.

554
00:39:42.503 --> 00:39:44.503 line:82%
I saw there was a tall man wearing...

555
00:39:44.584 --> 00:39:47.983 line:82%
a black coat standing in front of me.

556
00:39:48.896 --> 00:39:52.336 line:82%
I got up and went to him.
I asked him, "Yes?"

557
00:39:52.664 --> 00:39:55.303 line:82%
"Who are you? What are
you doing in my house?"

558
00:39:55.463 --> 00:39:56.743 line:82%
He turned towards me.

559
00:39:57.844 --> 00:40:00.803 line:82%
He had long hands.

560
00:40:01.123 --> 00:40:04.242 line:82%
His teeth were also black,
his eyes were red.

561
00:40:04.864 --> 00:40:06.382 line:82%
Is this an angel or a ghost?

562
00:40:07.060 --> 00:40:08.098 line:82%
Cleaning.

563
00:40:11.224 --> 00:40:12.423 line:82%
Such a big house to clean.

564
00:40:44.783 --> 00:40:46.983 line:82%
Hey, why are you still standing here?

565
00:40:47.303 --> 00:40:48.742 line:82%
Do you want to get beaten up again?

566
00:40:49.103 --> 00:40:52.069 line:82%
This was my house.
I don't have a place to stay.

567
00:40:52.094 --> 00:40:53.173 line:82%
Nor any work to do.

568
00:40:56.323 --> 00:40:59.202 line:82%
- Will you clean the house?
- I'll clean everything.

569
00:40:59.323 --> 00:41:03.042 line:82%
Don't steal anything or I'll
get you arrested by the police.

570
00:41:04.483 --> 00:41:07.722 line:82%
If you work properly, then
I'll give you Rs. 20 a day.

571
00:41:08.323 --> 00:41:11.243 line:82%
Give me Rs. 25. I'll be able
to buy a bottle of liquor then.

572
00:41:11.364 --> 00:41:14.202 line:82%
- Please. Please.
- Come on, pick up the broom.

573
00:41:14.323 --> 00:41:15.522 line:82%
- Come on, hurry up.
- Thank you.

574
00:41:15.944 --> 00:41:20.743 line:82%
Come on, start from
here and you are so dirty.

575
00:41:21.364 --> 00:41:22.403 line:82%
Go, have a bath first.

576
00:41:46.564 --> 00:41:47.603 line:82%
Yes.

577
00:42:06.684 --> 00:42:08.643 line:82%
Come on, give me Rs. 25. Hey.

578
00:42:20.203 --> 00:42:28.923 line:82%
Hey.

579
00:42:45.604 --> 00:42:46.923 line:82%
Go away. Go away.

580
00:42:51.364 --> 00:42:52.403 line:82%
Look at this.

581
00:42:54.403 --> 00:42:56.562 line:82%
- What are you looking at?
- Can't you see?

582
00:42:57.204 --> 00:42:59.523 line:82%
I am seeing everything.
You haven't cleaned anything.

583
00:42:59.683 --> 00:43:01.043 line:82%
There's so much work pending inside.

584
00:43:01.123 --> 00:43:02.442 line:82%
The things have to
be shifted. Come on.

585
00:43:34.723 --> 00:43:38.802 line:82%
- Oh, no.
- What are you doing?

586
00:43:39.043 --> 00:43:40.323 line:82%
The wind is blowing on its own.

587
00:43:40.644 --> 00:43:43.283 line:82%
The wind blows on its own.
What have you done?

588
00:43:43.440 --> 00:43:45.239 line:82%
You spread it all.
Who's going to clean it?

589
00:43:46.924 --> 00:43:47.963 line:82%
Don't sit.

590
00:43:52.363 --> 00:43:54.882 line:82%
Who asked you to sit?
Come on, get up.

591
00:43:58.998 --> 00:44:00.814 line:82%
Here? Wait a minute.
Wait a minute.

592
00:44:01.723 --> 00:44:03.363 line:82%
- Hit me.
- What?

593
00:44:03.444 --> 00:44:04.482 line:82%
No, hit me. Hit me. Hit me.

594
00:44:04.963 --> 00:44:06.347 line:82%
- Hit me.
- Alright.

595
00:44:06.496 --> 00:44:10.695 line:82%
- Yes.
- Who else is hitting me?

596
00:44:11.484 --> 00:44:13.242 line:82%
She hit me from here,
who hit me from here?

597
00:44:13.324 --> 00:44:15.443 line:82%
Come on, move the box
from there. Come on.

598
00:44:15.763 --> 00:44:18.563 line:82%
- Someone else is hitting me.
- Look at him.

599
00:44:19.204 --> 00:44:21.083 line:82%
Are you going to work or not?
Come on, go there.

600
00:44:21.324 --> 00:44:22.362 line:82%
- Work...
- Careful.

601
00:44:23.524 --> 00:44:26.043 line:82%
- Look at him.
- Who else is hitting me?

602
00:44:26.964 --> 00:44:29.442 line:82%
Who else is hitting me?

603
00:44:35.524 --> 00:44:37.002 line:82%
Come on, move it.

604
00:45:00.004 --> 00:45:04.323 line:82%
No, no, no, no. I...
I... it's not my fault.

605
00:45:04.404 --> 00:45:08.723 line:82%
It's... it's not my fault. Hold this.
Hold this. It's not my fault.

606
00:45:08.803 --> 00:45:12.843 line:82%
- You.
- It's not... She didn't even pay me.

607
00:45:14.644 --> 00:45:16.563 line:82%
I don't want to live in this house.

608
00:45:21.604 --> 00:45:23.442 line:82%
Aditya, I don't want to live here.

609
00:45:23.844 --> 00:45:26.922 line:82%
Ask your company to
arrange for some other place now.

610
00:45:27.183 --> 00:45:28.943 line:82%
Anjali. Anjali, you want
to leave such a nice house...

611
00:45:29.124 --> 00:45:31.002 line:82%
only because you didn't find a servant?

612
00:45:31.141 --> 00:45:32.180 line:82%
What about you?

613
00:45:32.269 --> 00:45:34.068 line:82%
You changed your house
and left in the ship.

614
00:45:34.444 --> 00:45:36.483 line:82%
It's me who has to
handle everything. Yes?

615
00:45:36.564 --> 00:45:38.643 line:82%
Wake up early in the morning,
dress up Banku, get ready...

616
00:45:38.724 --> 00:45:41.983 line:82%
prepare his tiffin...
Tiffin. Tiffin.

617
00:45:42.077 --> 00:45:43.315 line:82%
And he doesn't even finish his tiffin.

618
00:45:46.383 --> 00:45:47.822 line:82%
Do you have a problem with
the house or with the tiffin?

619
00:45:48.144 --> 00:45:51.343 line:82%
- What?
- You find it funny? No, laugh.

620
00:45:51.664 --> 00:45:52.822 line:82%
No, look, I am not laughing.

621
00:45:53.144 --> 00:45:54.862 line:82%
Look, I'll talk to mummy.

622
00:45:54.964 --> 00:45:56.973 line:82%
She'll come and stay with you
for a few days and help you.

623
00:45:57.119 --> 00:46:01.078 line:82%
You need not call mummy.
She anyway thinks I am lazy.

624
00:46:02.984 --> 00:46:05.342 line:82%
You just look for another house.
We won't stay here.

625
00:46:05.424 --> 00:46:07.142 line:82%
Okay. Okay. Give me a
day's time at least.

626
00:46:07.363 --> 00:46:08.922 line:82%
I'll think. I'll call you tomorrow.

627
00:46:15.523 --> 00:46:16.563 line:82%
When did you come?

628
00:46:16.963 --> 00:46:18.563 line:82%
When you were scolding papa.

629
00:46:19.044 --> 00:46:21.363 line:82%
I wasn't scolding him.
I was talking to him.

630
00:46:22.723 --> 00:46:24.642 line:82%
- And what are you doing?
- My homework.

631
00:46:25.084 --> 00:46:28.482 line:82%
- Homework. What's wrong with you?
- Nothing.

632
00:46:32.624 --> 00:46:34.543 line:82%
- You ate it all?
- Everything.

633
00:46:38.923 --> 00:46:41.802 line:82%
- Mama, are you angry?
- No.

634
00:46:42.904 --> 00:46:43.942 line:82%
Are you worried?

635
00:46:44.984 --> 00:46:48.183 line:82%
What to do? The
whole house is in a mess.

636
00:46:48.763 --> 00:46:53.202 line:82%
Don't worry, Mama. I'll clear
everything along with angel.

637
00:47:01.043 --> 00:47:03.802 line:82%
Where is he? Come on, show up.

638
00:47:21.564 --> 00:47:22.603 line:82%
What happened?

639
00:47:30.383 --> 00:47:32.902 line:82%
Okay, hide and seek.

640
00:48:05.224 --> 00:48:07.222 line:82%
Hey. Are you trying to scare me?

641
00:48:07.304 --> 00:48:08.863 line:82%
Quiet. Quiet. Mama might get up.

642
00:48:10.556 --> 00:48:13.435 line:82%
- Bhootnath, don't you take a bath?
- No.

643
00:48:14.124 --> 00:48:16.643 line:82%
Okay, show me your teeth... Show me.

644
00:48:18.283 --> 00:48:20.643 line:82%
Don't you brush your teeth?

645
00:48:22.204 --> 00:48:23.802 line:82%
