01:40:41.723 --> 01:40:45.043 line:82%
Father, this is Mr. Pradhan.
He owns a resort business.

1285
01:40:46.084 --> 01:40:47.523 line:82%
He is buying our house.

1286
01:40:48.323 --> 01:40:49.843 line:82%
We have already bought it,
Mr. Kailash Nath.

1287
01:40:50.636 --> 01:40:53.074 line:82%
Actually we are just
finishing the paper work tomorrow.

1288
01:40:53.952 --> 01:40:55.832 line:82%
Excuse me, Mr. Pradhan, but
this house is not for sale.

1289
01:40:57.524 --> 01:40:59.283 line:82%
But Vijay told me that...

1290
01:40:59.363 --> 01:41:01.123 line:82%
He is still a child.
It's not he who will decide...

1291
01:41:01.204 --> 01:41:02.883 line:82%
what has to be done with this house.

1292
01:41:03.643 --> 01:41:04.683 line:82%
Vijay, what is this?

1293
01:41:04.843 --> 01:41:05.963 line:82%
I am very sorry, Mr. Pradhan.

1294
01:41:06.094 --> 01:41:08.332 line:82%
You keep the papers ready.
We'll talk tomorrow.

1295
01:41:08.430 --> 01:41:09.949 line:82%
This house won't be sold.
Didn't you hear that?

1296
01:41:20.203 --> 01:41:22.362 line:82%
I had great difficulty in getting
such a nice price. And you...

1297
01:41:24.763 --> 01:41:26.123 line:82%
You are selling your house?

1298
01:41:26.327 --> 01:41:27.727 line:82%
What? What's so special
about this house, Father?

1299
01:41:29.326 --> 01:41:30.365 line:82%
What's so special about this house?

1300
01:41:34.925 --> 01:41:36.244 line:82%
You're asking me what's so
special about this house?

1301
01:41:39.163 --> 01:41:40.763 line:82%
You've spent your
childhood in this house.

1302
01:41:42.283 --> 01:41:43.563 line:82%
The first time you came
into your mother's lap...

1303
01:41:43.644 --> 01:41:45.483 line:82%
in this house...

1304
01:41:46.313 --> 01:41:48.551 line:82%
your mother's
happiness resides in this house.

1305
01:41:49.084 --> 01:41:52.602 line:82%
When you started to walk,
her... her smile...

1306
01:41:54.004 --> 01:41:55.162 line:82%
and when you used to fall sick...

1307
01:41:55.924 --> 01:41:57.763 line:82%
your mother used to
stay awake all night...

1308
01:41:57.844 --> 01:42:00.562 line:82%
and look after you.
That worry resides in this house.

1309
01:42:06.164 --> 01:42:10.162 line:82%
And when she fell sick and
was breathing her last...

1310
01:42:11.584 --> 01:42:14.023 line:82%
she was waiting for
her son to come home...

1311
01:42:14.104 --> 01:42:15.262 line:82%
that longing resides in this house.

1312
01:42:16.064 --> 01:42:18.063 line:82%
Father, you don't understand.

1313
01:42:19.084 --> 01:42:20.243 line:82%
All of us will go back to America.

1314
01:42:21.143 --> 01:42:23.583 line:82%
And then who's going to
look after such a big house?

1315
01:42:24.124 --> 01:42:24.831 line:82%
Let's sell it.

1316
01:42:24.856 --> 01:42:26.963 line:82%
Why should we sell it? All
of us will stay here together.

1317
01:42:27.380 --> 01:42:28.602 line:82%
No, Father, I can't stay here.

1318
01:42:28.764 --> 01:42:30.282 line:82%
And I can't even come back
from there every now and then.

1319
01:42:30.537 --> 01:42:32.283 line:82%
My work suffers,
Vibhut's studies suffer.

1320
01:42:32.364 --> 01:42:33.483 line:82%
And if he has to stay here...

1321
01:42:33.564 --> 01:42:34.803 line:82%
then why did you send him abroad?

1322
01:42:37.403 --> 01:42:41.443 line:82%
I sent him to study and
not to settle over there.

1323
01:42:42.744 --> 01:42:46.223 line:82%
Father, then come to America with us.

1324
01:42:47.124 --> 01:42:48.162 line:82%
There's nothing left here now.

1325
01:42:48.723 --> 01:42:50.483 line:82%
And anyway, what
will you do here alone?

1326
01:42:50.564 --> 01:42:51.683 line:82%
Even mother is no more now.

1327
01:42:55.604 --> 01:42:56.923 line:82%
Mother hasn't gone anywhere, Son.

1328
01:42:58.323 --> 01:43:01.682 line:82%
She is over here, in this very house.
She's listening to you.

1329
01:43:04.244 --> 01:43:10.163 line:82%
You go. Go and do your work.
I'll stay here and wonder...

1330
01:43:10.916 --> 01:43:16.915 line:82%
where I went wrong in nurturing you.

1331
01:43:26.124 --> 01:43:27.923 line:82%
This is really humiliating.

1332
01:43:28.184 --> 01:43:30.422 line:82%
I mean, do you have any
right on this house or not?

1333
01:43:32.184 --> 01:43:35.822 line:82%
I am sorry, Vijay, but I
can't stay here anymore.

1334
01:43:37.583 --> 01:43:40.263 line:82%
And no need to take him to America.

1335
01:43:41.624 --> 01:43:43.382 line:82%
He is not coming with us to America.

1336
01:43:50.224 --> 01:43:52.222 line:82%
Papa, I won't go.

1337
01:44:21.704 --> 01:44:22.742 line:82%
Father.

1338
01:44:28.983 --> 01:44:30.023 line:82%
Father, I...

1339
01:44:32.064 --> 01:44:35.063 line:82%
Never mind, dear.
People make mistakes.

1340
01:44:35.144 --> 01:44:36.782 line:82%
Every human makes mistakes.

1341
01:44:38.583 --> 01:44:40.423 line:82%
No, Father. We are going.

1342
01:44:42.744 --> 01:44:47.222 line:82%
You are going? What do
you mean by you are going?

1343
01:44:48.423 --> 01:44:49.903 line:82%
Father, we are going back to America.

1344
01:44:50.904 --> 01:44:52.502 line:82%
No, no, Vijay. Listen,
you... Where are you going?

1345
01:44:53.264 --> 01:44:55.022 line:82%
Father, you can come to
America whenever you want to.

1346
01:44:55.104 --> 01:44:56.623 line:82%
How... How will I
live without all of you?

1347
01:44:56.703 --> 01:44:57.782 line:82%
I'll keep sending you
the cheques every month.

1348
01:44:57.864 --> 01:44:58.903 line:82%
Vijay, listen to me.

1349
01:44:58.983 --> 01:45:00.023 line:82%
Grandpa, I won't go.

1350
01:45:00.104 --> 01:45:01.943 line:82%
No, dear. We won't
go anywhere. Nowhere.

1351
01:45:02.424 --> 01:45:04.022 line:82%
Daughter-in-law,
keep the luggage back.

1352
01:45:04.784 --> 01:45:06.343 line:82%
Vibhut, come on. Come down.

1353
01:45:06.423 --> 01:45:07.783 line:82%
No. I won't go.

1354
01:45:07.963 --> 01:45:09.083 line:82%
I said come down.

1355
01:45:09.163 --> 01:45:12.083 line:82%
- Vijay. - Vibhut, come here, Son.
Vibhut, come here.

1356
01:45:12.163 --> 01:45:14.763 line:82%
No, Vijay, if you can't
live without your son...

1357
01:45:14.844 --> 01:45:18.683 line:82%
then even I can't live
without my son. Don't go, Vijay.

1358
01:45:19.003 --> 01:45:20.043 line:82%
Don't go.

1359
01:45:35.004 --> 01:45:36.042 line:82%
What are you doing, Daughter-in-law?

1360
01:45:36.283 --> 01:45:39.443 line:82%
Grandpa, I won't go. Grandpa,
I won't go.

1361
01:45:39.523 --> 01:45:42.683 line:82%
Grandpa, I won't go.

1362
01:46:16.924 --> 01:46:17.963 line:82%
Vijay.

1363
01:46:28.163 --> 01:46:34.483 line:82%
Vijay. Vijay. Vijay.
Vijay, don't go, Vijay. Vijay.

1364
01:46:36.563 --> 01:46:41.362 line:82%
Vijay. Vijay. Vijay. Vijay.
Vijay. Vijay.

1365
01:46:42.944 --> 01:46:49.942 line:82%
Vijay, don't...
leave me and go, Vijay.

1366
01:48:10.843 --> 01:48:16.203 line:82%
I was lying right here,
but he didn't turn around...

1367
01:48:17.237 --> 01:48:23.156 line:82%
and see me even once.
Not even once.

1368
01:48:26.003 --> 01:48:28.683 line:82%
Since then, I've been
wandering in this... this house.

1369
01:48:30.333 --> 01:48:33.452 line:82%
I never allowed anyone
to live in this house.

1370
01:48:38.169 --> 01:48:45.047 line:82%
Then he came. My angel.

1371
01:48:48.497 --> 01:48:49.643 line:82%
He changed me.

1372
01:48:52.664 --> 01:48:54.023 line:82%
I forgot that I'm not alive.

1373
01:48:57.063 --> 01:48:58.262 line:82%
Does it hurt now?

1374
01:49:00.984 --> 01:49:05.222 line:82%
No, dear, it doesn't hurt now.

1375
01:49:06.924 --> 01:49:09.443 line:82%
How long will you keep
wandering like that?

1376
01:49:12.024 --> 01:49:13.982 line:82%
Why don't you forgive your son?

1377
01:49:14.144 --> 01:49:19.382 line:82%
No. Never. I won't forgive him.

1378
01:49:24.004 --> 01:49:27.483 line:82%
He left me, but I will never
leave this house. I won't.

1379
01:49:29.104 --> 01:49:31.023 line:82%
Even if I have to wander
here for the next 100 lives.

1380
01:49:33.403 --> 01:49:39.642 line:82%
100 lives. Now only you
people will live in this house.

1381
01:49:44.284 --> 01:49:49.083 line:82%
Banku will stay here, forever.

1382
01:49:51.164 --> 01:49:53.282 line:82%
You people can't leave
this place. No.

1383
01:49:54.003 --> 01:49:55.123 line:82%
You people can't go.

1384
01:50:13.823 --> 01:50:16.623 line:82%
Is he still here?

1385
01:50:19.444 --> 01:50:22.243 line:82%
So where is he right now?

1386
01:50:36.003 --> 01:50:38.162 line:82%
Kailash Nath used to love his son.

1387
01:50:39.303 --> 01:50:42.542 line:82%
He offered many prayers
for him in this temple.

1388
01:50:44.724 --> 01:50:47.522 line:82%
Now he has got attached to your son.

1389
01:50:47.884 --> 01:50:49.563 line:82%
Priest, that's what
we are fearing that...

1390
01:50:50.154 --> 01:50:52.043 line:82%
what if he does anything to Banku...

1391
01:50:52.123 --> 01:50:55.242 line:82%
Oh, no. No. Kailash has
never caused any harm to anyone.

1392
01:50:56.224 --> 01:50:57.343 line:82%
He won't do anything.

1393
01:50:57.743 --> 01:51:00.262 line:82%
Then what... What should we do now?

1394
01:51:00.704 --> 01:51:01.743 line:82%
Post death ceremony.

1395
01:51:03.303 --> 01:51:05.263 line:82%
We will have to do it for
his soul to rest in peace.

1396
01:51:05.864 --> 01:51:08.371 line:82%
But only his son can do that.

1397
01:51:09.004 --> 01:51:10.403 line:82%
Yes. He should be the one to do it.

1398
01:51:11.724 --> 01:51:13.563 line:82%
Anyway this rite
hasn't been performed...

1399
01:51:13.644 --> 01:51:16.083 line:82%
after Kailash's death.
Who would have done it?

1400
01:51:16.684 --> 01:51:17.723 line:82%
His son was abroad.

1401
01:51:18.564 --> 01:51:20.123 line:82%
Well, I have heard that
he is here these days.

1402
01:51:21.123 --> 01:51:24.242 line:82%
Then I will meet and talk to him.

1403
01:51:26.710 --> 01:51:29.029 line:82%
If you heed my advice then your son...

1404
01:51:29.204 --> 01:51:31.643 line:82%
can give Kailash his salvation.

1405
01:51:32.764 --> 01:51:34.203 line:82%
God answers to children's prayers.

1406
01:51:35.183 --> 01:51:37.423 line:82%
God will surely accept his prayers.

1407
01:51:45.983 --> 01:51:47.023 line:82%
Vijay...

1408
01:51:50.124 --> 01:51:51.162 line:82%
- Aditya.
- Hi.

1409
01:51:55.884 --> 01:51:57.522 line:82%
I always come here when I come to Goa.

1410
01:51:58.444 --> 01:52:00.123 line:82%
You come to Goa, but you don't go home.

1411
01:52:01.204 --> 01:52:02.243 line:82%
You stay there.

1412
01:52:03.382 --> 01:52:05.181 line:82%
And you want to throw us out of there.

1413
01:52:06.444 --> 01:52:07.523 line:82%
I am bringing down Nath Villa.

1414
01:52:08.883 --> 01:52:11.522 line:82%
This time I will sell the
land and leave Goa forever.

1415
01:52:12.863 --> 01:52:14.902 line:82%
No house, no ghost.

1416
01:52:16.943 --> 01:52:22.702 line:82%
Not a ghost, but a spirit.
A disgruntled spirit of your father.

1417
01:52:23.323 --> 01:52:25.883 line:82%
Disgruntled? Dissatisfied.

1418
01:52:27.271 --> 01:52:29.430 line:82%
Father has always been
dissatisfied with me.

1419
01:52:30.684 --> 01:52:31.803 line:82%
He could never understand me.

1420
01:52:31.984 --> 01:52:34.743 line:82%
Or perhaps you could
never understand him.

1421
01:52:36.364 --> 01:52:40.043 line:82%
Vijay, your father is
attached to that house.

1422
01:52:40.803 --> 01:52:43.043 line:82%
He doesn't want the house full of...

1423
01:52:43.124 --> 01:52:44.963 line:82%
your mother's
memories to be demolished.

1424
01:52:45.804 --> 01:52:48.843 line:82%
Perhaps that's why his
soul has still been wandering.

1425
01:52:50.444 --> 01:52:53.083 line:82%
Look, Aditya, I don't
believe in all this.

1426
01:52:54.064 --> 01:52:56.383 line:82%
And I find it really funny that...

1427
01:52:56.464 --> 01:52:58.957 line:82%
my father's soul
troubles everyone other than me.

1428
01:53:00.064 --> 01:53:03.823 line:82%
Doesn't trouble, just
gives a sense of his presence.

1429
01:53:04.749 --> 01:53:06.668 line:82%
You know a lot about my father.

1430
01:53:08.178 --> 01:53:09.698 line:82%
The day you were leaving the house...

1431
01:53:09.904 --> 01:53:12.022 line:82%
your father went
after his son to stop him.

1432
01:53:12.277 --> 01:53:13.756 line:82%
And he slipped and
fell down and maybe...

1433
01:53:14.087 --> 01:53:15.485 line:82%
maybe even screamed.

1434
01:53:16.784 --> 01:53:19.143 line:82%
But his son didn't turn
around and look at him even once.

1435
01:53:19.317 --> 01:53:21.596 line:82%
- That was an accident.
- That's what you think.

1436
01:53:21.774 --> 01:53:23.933 line:82%
What do you want to say?
I killed my father?

1437
01:53:24.464 --> 01:53:27.022 line:82%
You don't know anything.
I was not wrong.

1438
01:53:27.184 --> 01:53:28.743 line:82%
He couldn't even understand
such a small thing that I...

1439
01:53:28.823 --> 01:53:30.543 line:82%
Now you aren't able to
understand such a small thing.

1440
01:53:31.024 --> 01:53:33.583 line:82%
Vijay. Vijay, all you
need to do is apologize.

1441
01:53:33.804 --> 01:53:34.842 line:82%
That, too, to your father.

1442
01:53:35.344 --> 01:53:36.677 line:82%
Just come home and
apologize to him once.

1443
01:53:36.785 --> 01:53:38.224 line:82%
Maybe his soul will rest in peace.

1444
01:53:38.684 --> 01:53:40.683 line:82%
You have come to tell
me what I should do?

1445
01:53:40.796 --> 01:53:44.112 line:82%
No, I have come to
inform you that we have kept...

1446
01:53:44.377 --> 01:53:47.183 line:82%
veneration so that your
father's soul rests in peace.

1447
01:53:47.243 --> 01:53:49.762 line:82%
We are performing a
post death ceremony.

1448
01:53:49.844 --> 01:53:51.403 line:82%
Post death ceremonies
aren't performed in America...

1449
01:53:51.584 --> 01:53:53.263 line:82%
but people still attain salvation.

1450
01:53:54.524 --> 01:53:55.883 line:82%
A son performs this
rite for his father.

1451
01:53:56.283 --> 01:53:58.802 line:82%
Hey, so you do it.
Prayer veneration and all.

1452
01:53:58.884 --> 01:53:59.843 line:82%
Do as you please.

1453
01:54:00.324 --> 01:54:01.922 line:82%
I am coming to take the
house keys the next day.

1454
01:54:03.782 --> 01:54:08.637 line:82%
Okay, I will surely keep
some offerings for you.

1455
01:54:14.384 --> 01:54:16.063 line:82%
Anyway, Vijay, even I didn't
believe in all these things.

1456
01:54:17.743 --> 01:54:22.902 line:82%
But I agree that some things
are always left incomplete.

1457
01:54:25.164 --> 01:54:28.643 line:82%
This veneration, too, will
be incomplete without you.

1458
01:54:43.144 --> 01:54:45.624 line:82%
Tomorrow, we are keeping a small...

1459
01:54:45.687 --> 01:54:47.143 line:82%
veneration for your Bhootnath.

1460
01:54:47.924 --> 01:54:49.922 line:82%
Really? Ls it his birthday?

1461
01:54:52.563 --> 01:54:56.563 line:82%
For his rebirth, for his...
salvation.

1462
01:54:57.503 --> 01:54:59.263 line:82%
Salvation? What's that?

1463
01:55:03.004 --> 01:55:04.043 line:82%
Come here, Banku.

1464
01:55:04.583 --> 01:55:07.903 line:82%
Look, like you have gone
from grade one to grade two...

1465
01:55:08.384 --> 01:55:11.183 line:82%
similarly with this veneration,
your Bhootnath...

1466
01:55:11.864 --> 01:55:14.628 line:82%
will become a star
angel from an ordinary one.

1467
01:55:14.878 --> 01:55:16.997 line:82%
Star angel. I will
just go and inform him.

1468
01:55:17.128 --> 01:55:18.527 line:82%
Hey, Banku... Banku.

1469
01:55:25.444 --> 01:55:27.963 line:82%
Bhootnath, you know I am keeping...

1470
01:55:28.144 --> 01:55:30.663 line:82%
veneration for your salvation.

1471
01:55:35.584 --> 01:55:36.622 line:82%
Salvation?

1472
01:55:37.240 --> 01:55:41.512 line:82%
Yes. Like I went from grade
one to grade two, similarly...

1473
01:55:41.686 --> 01:55:44.309 line:82%
you will become a star
angel from an ordinary one.

1474
01:55:46.943 --> 01:55:47.983 line:82%
Just like my grandpa.

1475
01:55:53.104 --> 01:55:55.743 line:82%
- Look there.
- Let me look.

1476
01:55:57.743 --> 01:55:58.942 line:82%
Let me look at you
to my heart's content.

1477
01:56:00.823 --> 01:56:03.702 line:82%
I don't know whether I will be
able to meet you again or not.

1478
01:56:04.124 --> 01:56:07.283 line:82%
Why? You will also look at me
like grandpa does, won't you?

1479
01:56:08.324 --> 01:56:11.803 line:82%
I will. I will
only be watching you.

1480
01:56:13.604 --> 01:56:15.283 line:82%
Promise me that you will
also look at me every day.

1481
01:56:16.083 --> 01:56:19.043 line:82%
Promise. But what
if the clouds come?

1482
01:56:21.564 --> 01:56:23.442 line:82%
Not even God can come between us.

1483
01:56:25.404 --> 01:56:27.683 line:82%
Promise me that you will
never trouble your mother.

1484
01:56:28.304 --> 01:56:30.063 line:82%
If she doesn't give me
an ice cream, then I will.

1485
01:56:32.384 --> 01:56:35.983 line:82%
Promise me that you will
never leave your parents.

1486
01:56:36.623 --> 01:56:39.103 line:82%
So many promises?
That, too, at one go?

1487
01:56:39.824 --> 01:56:41.023 line:82%
Bhootnath, you will
just get salvation...

1488
01:56:41.204 --> 01:56:43.883 line:82%
you won't be going anywhere.

1489
01:56:46.624 --> 01:56:49.983 line:82%
Okay, but the last...

1490
01:56:51.843 --> 01:56:53.603 line:82%
Promise me that you will
never fight with anyone...

1491
01:56:53.684 --> 01:56:56.402 line:82%
and you will always forgive everyone.

1492
01:56:57.204 --> 01:57:00.683 line:82%
- I will not forgive anyone.
- No, it's necessary to forgive.

1493
01:57:01.464 --> 01:57:03.303 line:82%
Like dirty clothes
become clean after a wash...

1494
01:57:04.284 --> 01:57:06.707 line:82%
your heart becomes clear
